r.<br></li><li> Complex characters with their own secrets, desires, and pursuits.<br></li><li> Multiple endings based on the player’s choices and actions.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332370/extras/23440d19bf5113d6abd851776d2339bb.avif?t=1666990957\" width=159 height=500 /></span>",
